data.description: Affordable Bungalow close to Beautiful Oregon Coast Beaches & State Parks. This 2 bedroom, 1 bath would make a great investment or vacation property. This home features a nice sized 50x120 ft. fully fenced yard, large Carport and sliding glass door off the primary bedroom to back patio. Plenty of room to park an RV or boat. Home is located just a few blocks to public boat ramp, fishing and crabbing. Make your appointment Today!
